*mysql-5.0.16 (23 Nov 2005)

  23 Nov 2005; Francesco Riosa <vivo@gentoo.org> files/mysql-slot.rc6,
  -mysql-4.0.26-r30.ebuild, mysql-4.1.15-r30.ebuild,
